  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u200c\u0dad\u0ddd\u0dbb\u0db1 \u0daf\u0dd2\u0db1 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dba\u0db8 \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The date for electing the President will be fixed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Yesterday afternoon, parliamentary party leaders decided to invite nominations from members of parliament within three days to appoint a new president if President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa resigns.",
        "Accordingly, it has been decided to call for nominations from Friday the 15th and to end the call for nominations on Tuesday next week.",
        "After closing the nominations, the Parliament will meet on Wednesday and Thursday next week and hold a vote to elect the President.",
        "In the meantime, it has been decided that the party leaders will meet and discuss the economic situation of the country tomorrow morning and hold another discussion in the afternoon.",
        "The party leaders have decided to invite the representatives of the struggle to the discussion held in the evening."
      ],
